articles.title: Biden set to discuss wrongfully detained Americans during White House Correspondents Dinner - CNN
articles.description: President Joe Biden appeared at the White House Correspondents Dinner on Saturday, marking his first time at the black-tie gathering in Washington since he announced the launch of his reelection campaign earlier this week.
